\maketitle

\begin{abstract}
  A class of shape-invariant bound-state problems which represent
  two-level systems are introduced. It is shown that the
  coupled-channel Hamiltonians obtained correspond to the
  generalization of the Jaynes-Cummings Hamiltonian.   
\end{abstract}

